{"article_id":"4qPeavKTFThPB0y3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump will stick with the same list of potential nominees for the next Supreme Court vacancy ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"he told The in an exclusive interview","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"in which he also waved aside the lack of a honeymoon from Capitol Hill ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Republicans are \" going to get there \"","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and Democrats are still smarting","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"over losing an election","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"they thought","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"they couldn ' t lose .","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"Speaking in the Oval Office ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"a repeal of Obamacare would have passed the House last week","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"if Republican leaders had put it up for a vote .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"He now expects a vote early in May ,","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"which","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"he acknowledged","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"is outside the 100-day time frame","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"he had hoped for","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"but still much shorter than the 15 months","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"it took President Obama","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"to have the national health care bill enacted .","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"He also said","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"he expects the near-universal opposition to his agenda from congressional Democrats to wane .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Reflecting on his first weeks ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"the businessman turned statesman took pride in having upended traditional procedures in Washington .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"he has already notched foreign policy successes","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that eluded Mr. Obama","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"- such as the release of Egyptian-American charity worker Aya Hijazi from detention in Egypt -","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"and has made his mark at home with the confirmation of Supreme Court Justice Neil Gorsuch .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" You ' ll have hundreds of cases","depth":14},{"id":31,"text":"decided by 5-4 ,","depth":14},{"id":32,"text":"and you got that .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"So that ' s a great legacy , \"","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"the president said ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"noting","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"that at 49 , Justice Gorsuch has decades of important decisions ahead of him .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Mr. Trump shook the election campaign last year","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"when he announced a list of 21 potential Supreme Court nominees ,","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"selected with the help of the Federalist Society and The Heritage Foundation .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"The list was an instant hit with conservatives","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and helped cement the candidate ' s support among the Republican base .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"\" It ' s a great list .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"From the moment","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"I put that list out ,","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"it solved that problem .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"And I was proud to say","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"it was my idea , \"","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"he has heard rumors","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that one of the justices will retire","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"when the current court session ends in June","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"but that he doesn ' t have any inside knowledge .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" I don ' t know .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"I have a lot of respect for Justice Kennedy ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"but I just don ' t know , \"","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Mr. Trump said ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"referring to the senior member of the bench , Justice Anthony M. Kennedy .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"\" I don ' t like talking about it .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"I ' ve heard the same rumors","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"that a lot of people have heard .","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"And I have a lot of respect for that gentleman , a lot . \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"conservative voters should be assured","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that his next choice will be \" really talented and of our views. \"","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Asked specifically","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"whether he would pick from the list of candidates","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"he put forward in the campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Mr. Trump was unequivocal :","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" Yes , \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"he said ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"\" That list was a big thing . \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Democrats rallied near-unanimous opposition","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and mounted a filibuster in the fight over Justice Gorsuch ,","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"forcing Senate Republican leaders to trigger the \" nuclear option \" and take a shortcut","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to change the rules .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"It was just one of the areas","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"where Democrats have vowed to resist Mr. Trump at every turn .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"The president took a dealmaker ' s view of the obstructions","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"he had faced on Capitol Hill , particularly from Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer , a fellow New Yorker .","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"Last week ,","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"as the federal government teetered on the verge of a partial shutdown ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"Republican leaders said","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"Mr. Schumer was refusing to even talk to Mr. Trump","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"- particularly about permitting any money for Mr. Trump ' s Mexico border wall .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"The president , though , said","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"Mr. Schumer is coming to the table .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"\" He ' s negotiating .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"I spoke to him three days ago .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"He ' s negotiating from a standpoint","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"where the Democrats have been decimated , \"","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"the president said .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"\" They thought","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"they were going to win .","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"It ' s almost impossible for the Democrats to lose .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"And I think","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"we ' re much stronger today","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"than I was on election night .","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"You ' ve seen some polls come out","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"where I ' m stronger today","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"than I was on election night .","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"So they ' re not happy ,","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"they ' re very angry . \"","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"The Senate Democratic leader , though , said Sunday","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"that it is Mr. Trump who isn ' t ready to talk about serious issues on Democrats ' terms .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"\" On the issues so far","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"- taxes and health care -","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"he doesn ' t consult us at all , \"","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Mr. Schumer said on \" Fox News Sunday. \"","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"\" He puts together a plan","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"that is very hard-right , special-interest [ and ] wealth-oriented","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"and says","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"the way","depth":14},{"id":115,"text":"to be bipartisan","depth":14},{"id":116,"text":"is to just support his plan .","depth":13},{"id":117,"text":"That ' s not the way","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"America works . \"","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"Mr. Trump has struggled to forge unity within Republican ranks , too ,","depth":4},{"id":120,"text":"hindering his efforts","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"to notch early-term accomplishments .","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"But the president said","depth":5},{"id":123,"text":"he wasn ' t put off by the lack of a honeymoon even from his own party .","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"\" It ' s a tight margin .","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"These are really terrific people ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"and they ' ve been very good to me in the sense","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"that they say ,","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"' We want to do this for our president , ' \"","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"that includes both the right and the centrists .","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"\" I will say ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"they have their views ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"their views are somewhat spread out ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"I believe","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"they ' re going to get there , \"","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"pivoting to the debate over repealing Obamacare .","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"\" I believe","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"over the next week or two or three ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"I said","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"take your time .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"You said","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"Obama had a honeymoon .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"The truth is Obamacare took 17 months","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"to get approved .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"I only started working this a month and a half in .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"We could have taken a vote today ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"I think","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"it could have made it ,","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"but who wants to take the chance ?","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"So we ' ll wait till next week .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"This is an artificial barrier ,","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"which I helped cause to a certain extent ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"but we ' ve done a lot . \"","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"A constant during Mr. Trump ' s first 100 days in office has been his running battle with the media .","depth":3},{"id":157,"text":"Despite his efforts","depth":6},{"id":158,"text":"to bypass the media","depth":7},{"id":159,"text":"by posting frequent messages on Twitter ,","depth":7},{"id":160,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":6},{"id":161,"text":"his job approval ratings would be better","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"if he weren ' t confronting a steady stream of what he calls \" fake news . \"","depth":7},{"id":163,"text":"\" I think","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"I ' m polling really , really well ,","depth":6},{"id":165,"text":"considering","depth":7},{"id":166,"text":"if you watch television .","depth":7},{"id":167,"text":"... You ' d say ,","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"' How can this guy be at 48 percent ? ' \"","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"\" Anywhere in that [ range ] ,","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"how can you do that","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"when every single story is a hit ? \"","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"One of Mr. Trump ' s biggest foreign policy challenges so far has been the threat","depth":4},{"id":174,"text":"posed by North Korea ' s ballistic missile and nuclear weapons programs .","depth":4},{"id":175,"text":"White House National Security Adviser H.R . McMaster said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"that the U.S. would pay for the $ 1 billion THAAD missile defense system in South Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":177,"text":"despite Mr. Trump ' s comments to The Times two days earlier","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"about making Seoul pick up the tab .","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"\" What I told our South Korean counterpart","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"is","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"until any renegotiation ,","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"that the deals in place ,","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"we ' ll adhere to our word , \"","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"Mr. McMaster said on \" Fox News Sunday . \"","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s comments had caused unease in Seoul ,","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"which was already nervous about the belligerent exchanges between Washington and Pyongyang .","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"Mr. McMaster sought to reassure the ally in call earlier Sunday","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"and told Fox","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"that he was not contradicting Mr. Trump .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"\" The last thing","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"I would ever do","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"is contradict the president of the United States .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"And that ' s not what it was , \"","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":195,"text":"\" What the president has asked us to do , is to look across all of our alliances and to have appropriate burden-sharing , responsibility-sharing .","depth":7},{"id":196,"text":"We ' re looking at that with our great ally South Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"we ' re looking at that with NATO . \"","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"Mr. McMaster also stressed","depth":6},{"id":199,"text":"that North Korea poses a \" grave threat \" to the U.S. and allies in the region","depth":7},{"id":200,"text":"and that Mr. Trump was determined to resolve the issue \" one way or another . \"","depth":7},{"id":201,"text":"Mr. Trump also said in the interview with The Times","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"that he wants to renegotiate or withdraw from the U.S.-Korea Free Trade Agreement","depth":9},{"id":203,"text":"known as Korus ,","depth":9},{"id":204,"text":"which enters a review period this week .","depth":8},{"id":205,"text":"The current version ,","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"first begun under the George W. Bush administration ,","depth":9},{"id":207,"text":"took effect in March 2012 under the Obama administration .","depth":8},{"id":208,"text":"\" It ' s been a very bad deal for the United States ,","depth":9},{"id":209,"text":"negotiated by","depth":10},{"id":210,"text":"[ former Secretary of State ]","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"Hillary Clinton , \"","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":425,"left":368,"right":424,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":368,"left":331,"right":367,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":331,"left":249,"right":330,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":249,"left":221,"right":248,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":221,"left":0,"right":220,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":214,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":219,"left":3,"right":218,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":4,"right":217,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":217,"left":5,"right":216,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":6,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":248,"left":234,"right":247,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":234,"left":232,"right":233,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":232,"left":224,"right":231,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":222,"right":223,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":222,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":223,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":13,"right":230,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":230,"left":225,"right":229,"relation":"same-unit","nucleari